    "body": "The author of https://github.com/OpenZeppelin/openzeppelin-contracts/issues/2880 (same issue, but in OpenZeppelin) suggests the bug may be hardware/OS based?\r\n\r\nWould be nice to eliminate that. Can anyone confirm whether the following works for them:\r\n\r\n```\r\ngit clone git@github.com:OpenZeppelin/openzeppelin-contracts.git\r\ncd openzeppelin-contracts\r\nnpm install\r\nnpm run test\r\n```\r\n\r\nAnd if so, indicate computer & OS?\r\n\r\nI can confirm this is happening for me on my Mac with the following specs:\r\n\r\n```\r\nOS: Big Sur 11.5.2\r\nModel Name: MacBook Pro\r\nModel Identifier: MacBookPro15,3\r\nProcessor Name: 6-Core Intel Core i9\r\nMemory: 32 GB\r\n```",
